n\n\n\n<p>Enable a Two-Factor Authentication on all your important accounts like email, social media, or banking. Why? Whilst moving abroad you will use a lot of unsecured public WiFi. Prevent your accounts from being hacked by simply enabling two-factor authentication that most online services offer. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104553\/travel-from-home-plan-trips-1080x721.jpg\" alt=\"travel from home plan trips\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"travel from home plan trips\" class=\"wp-image-49738 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104553\/travel-from-home-plan-trips-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104553\/travel-from-home-plan-trips-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104553\/travel-from-home-plan-trips-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104553\/travel-from-home-plan-trips-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104553\/travel-from-home-plan-trips-450x300.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104553\/travel-from-home-plan-trips-1536x1025.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104553\/travel-from-home-plan-trips-30x20.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104553\/travel-from-home-plan-trips-163x109.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104553\/travel-from-home-plan-trips-270x180.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104553\/travel-from-home-plan-trips-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104553\/travel-from-home-plan-trips-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104553\/travel-from-home-plan-trips-1440x961.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104553\/travel-from-home-plan-trips.jpg 1920w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104553\/travel-from-home-plan-trips-30x20.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/01\/23104553\/travel-from-home-plan-trips-1080x721.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-simlock\">Simlock<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Staying connected in another country is useful for many things, like reading the map, or making an emergency phone call. You will need to get a local sim card at your new destination, however, your current provider might not allow the phone to be used on another network. This is called simlock.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Most phones are not sim-locked anymore, however, check with your provider. The specific unlock instructions differ according to your phone model.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103257\/how-to-move-abroad-simlock-2.jpg\" alt=\"how to move abroad simlock\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"324\" alt=\"how to move abroad simlock\" class