f=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103257\/how-to-move-abroad-simlock-2.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-universal-adapter\">Universal Adapter<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A universal adaptor is a power plug that allows you to put your plug into the socket pretty much anywhere around the world. It&#x2019;s an absolute must-have, and it will save you from having problems charging your devices when you arrive at your new destination. (<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/universal-travel-adapter\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Get a travel adapter here<\/a>)<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103246\/move-abroad-universal-adapter.jpg\" alt=\"move abroad universal adapter\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"300\" alt=\"move abroad universal adapter\" class=\"wp-image-52993 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103246\/move-abroad-universal-adapter.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103246\/move-abroad-universal-adapter-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103246\/move-abroad-universal-adapter-600x400.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103246\/move-abroad-universal-adapter-800x534.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103246\/move-abroad-universal-adapter-1080x721.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103246\/move-abroad-universal-ada