t sort out all of your visa paperwork and accommodation, as part of the job offer.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Learn:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/how-to-make-money-online\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">How to Make Money Online: 14 Jobs &amp; Where to Find Them<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103230\/how-to-move-abroad-co-working.jpg\" alt=\"how to move abroad co-working\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"how to move abroad co-working\" class=\"wp-image-53008 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103230\/how-to-move-abroad-co-working.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103230\/how-to-move-abroad-co-working-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103230\/how-to-move-abroad-co-working-600x750.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103230\/how-to-move-abroad-co-working-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103230\/how-to-move-abroad-co-working-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103230\/how-to-move-abroad-co-working-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103230\/how-to-move-abroad-co-working-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103230\/how-to-move-abroad-co-working-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103230\/how-to-move-abroad-co-working-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103230\/how-to-move-abroad-co-working-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103230\/how-to-move-abroad-co-working-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103230\/how-to-move-abroad-co-working-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103230\/how-to-move-abroad-co-working-1152x1440.jpg 1152w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103230\/how-to-move-abroad-co-working-24x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103230\/how-to-move-abroad-co-working.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 id=\"h-working-online-in-another-country\">Working Online in Another Country<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Working online in another country as a digital nomad has become extremely popular. A <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/become-digital-nomad\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">digital nomad<\/a> is someone who performs their work online. This can be as a freelancer or while working for another company. It is very convenient to already have a steady income when moving abroad. Digital nomads tend to work at co-working spaces in order to meet other people who work online.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tip \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tip\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read more:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/become-digital-nomad\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">How to Become a Digital Nomad: Travel &amp; Make Money<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<h4 id=\"h-finding-a-job-abroad\">Finding a Job Abroad<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>On the other hand, finding a job <em>after<\/em> you move abroad can also be beneficial, as it can give you the time to see what the options are in person. Make sure, however, that you are always aware of the job requirements. For example, if you&#x2019;re moving to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/italy\/\">Italy<\/a> you&#x2019;ll need to learn Italian for most jobs.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103304\/how-to-move-abroad-digital-nomad.jpg\" alt=\"how to move abroad digital nomad\"><\/noscript><img width=\"254\" height=\"338\" alt=\"how to move abroad digital nomad\" class=\"wp-image-52988 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1440px) 100vw, 1440px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103304\/how-to-move-abroad-digital-nomad.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/231033