cide to rent an apartment before or after you move abroad, it&#x2019;s a good idea to use local knowledge to find out the best neighborhoods. A good way of doing this is by asking questions in Facebook communities, through rental agencies, houseshare websites, or by walking around the city once you arrive.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103239\/how-to-move-abroad-city-626x810.jpg\" alt=\"how to move abroad city\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"how to move abroad city\" class=\"wp-image-53004 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 626px) 100vw, 626px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103239\/how-to-move-abroad-city-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103239\/how-to-move-abroad-city-300x388.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103239\/how-to-move-abroad-city-600x776.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103239\/how-to-move-abroad-city-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103239\/how-to-move-abroad-city-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103239\/how-to-move-abroad-city-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103239\/how-to-move-abroad-city-126x163.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103239\/how-to-move-abroad-city-139x180.jpg 139w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103239\/how-to-move-abroad-city-594x768.jpg 594w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103239\/how