 need those copies of your documentation we mentioned earlier. It&#x2019;s a good idea to research the average cost of bills before you move abroad. This way you can put some money aside to budget for the first few months of living.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-make-friends-abroad\">Make Friends Abroad<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>One of the best parts of choosing to move abroad is making new friends! Whether it&#x2019;s other like-minded travelers or locals who want to show you how life works, some really fun times are waiting for you in your new life abroad.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Think of the ways you might be able to meet people and research events and meetups before you arrive. Great ways to meet people include practicing sports, going to a language exchange, a painting class, or using apps like &#x2018;meetup&#x2019; to find new friends.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103020\/travel-meet-friends.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"331\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-53487 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103020\/travel-meet-friends.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103020\/travel-meet-friends-800x588.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103020\/travel-meet-friends-1080x794.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103020\/travel-meet-friends-450x331.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103020\/travel-meet-friends-30x22.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103020\/travel-meet-friends-163x120.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103020\/travel-meet-friends-245x180.jpg 245w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103020\/travel-meet-friends-768x565.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103020\/travel-meet-friends-1024x753.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103020\/travel-meet-friends-1440x1059.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103020\/travel-meet-friends-300x221.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103020\/travel-meet-friends-600x441.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103020\/travel-meet-friends-82x60.jpg 82w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103020\/travel-meet-friends-122x90.jpg 122w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103020\/travel-meet-friends-30x22.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/03\/23103020\/travel-meet-friends.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-prepare-for-homesickness-after-moving-abroad\">Prepare for Homesickness After Moving Abroad<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>When you first move abroad, it is not unusual to suffer from culture shock and homesickness. In order to prevent you missing the comforts of home, bring items like your favorite food and drink, and family photos.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>It&#x2019;s also a good idea to schedule regular phone calls with your family and friends from home, to help you through the tricky initial stages of your move abroad.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"Prepare to Move Abroad So you&#x2019;re considering packing up your belongings and moving abroad to start the journey of a lifetime. But what are the steps in starting this new and exciting adventure?&#xA0;Here&#x2019;s what you need to prepare: Your Belongings and Subscriptions Belongings You may have numerous possessions that you need to consider what to [&hellip;]","protected":false},"author":6,"featured_media":53492,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_relevanssi_hide_post":"","_relevanssi_pin_for_all":"","_relevanssi_pin_keywords":"","_relevanssi_unpin_keywords":"","_relevanssi_related_keywords":"","_relevanssi_related_include_ids":"","_relevanssi_related_exclude_ids":"","_relevanssi_related_no_append":"","_relevanssi_related_not_related":"","_relevanssi_related_posts":"9763,7957,14217,17738,9293,4651"},"categories":[7172,7175,30],"tags":[],"acf":[],"yoast_head":"<!-- This site is optimized with the Yoast SEO Premium plugin v19.3 (Yoast SEO v19.7.1) - https:\/\/yoast.com\/wordpress\/plugins\/seo\/ -->\n<title>How to Move Abroad: Tips for Moving to Another Country!<\/title>\n<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Looking to move abroad? Follow this step-by-step guide on the practicalities of moving abroad and how to live the life of your dreams.\" \/>\n<meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow, max-snippet:-1, max-image-preview:large, max-video-preview:-1\" \/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/how-to-move-abroad\/\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"article\" \/>\n<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"How to Move Abroad: Tips for Moving to Another Cou